    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Starsim 是一款科幻多体裁的计算机游戏，结合了实时暂停制战斗、文字冒险和回合制战术。在这里，你可以成为英雄、商人、拾荒者、雇佣兵或海盗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家探索部分随机生成的星系，每个区域都包含多颗星星和行星。这导致一个拥有数百个行星的宇宙，每个行星都有自己的经济、政府和对玩家的看法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏不受边界限制，允许玩家影响分支情节。与此同时，更大、更广阔的游戏世界将自己生活和发展。在 Starsim 中，玩家将有机会测试他们的技能，不仅在太空中，还在回合制战术中。 <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166890/extras/2cda2539506facf41cd6d0baec1fcfb8.webp?t=1763028353\" width=605 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的一个特色是模拟飞船控制，包括管理机组人员、修改飞船以及控制武器、引擎和护盾等系统。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166890/extras/792c700ad92c60c58c2fc34a4a24694b.poster.avif?t=1763028353\" width=854 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166890/extras/792c700ad92c60c58c2fc34a4a24694b.webm?t=1763028353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166890/extras/792c700ad92c60c58c2fc34a4a24694b.mp4?t=1763028353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Starsim 中，玩家将控制一艘宇宙飞船和机组人员，完成各种任务，穿越星系。他将能够选择任务、探索新的行星、星系和星区。参与在陆地和太空中与敌人的战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166890/extras/ae20a0ad037c5ce9a84b64c9d2a37e3b.poster.avif?t=1763028353\" width=854 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166890/extras/ae20a0ad037c5ce9a84b64c9d2a37e3b.webm?t=1763028353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166890/extras/ae20a0ad037c5ce9a84b64c9d2a37e3b.mp4?t=1763028353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，玩家将有机会展示他们的领导潜力，并在各种情况下管理团队，如任务和战斗。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166890/extras/907175787de8863dfece134f5a652f4e.poster.avif?t=1763028353\" width=854 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166890/extras/907175787de8863dfece134f5a652f4e.webm?t=1763028353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166890/extras/907175787de8863dfece134f5a652f4e.mp4?t=1763028353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >总的来说，Starsim 是不同体裁和机制的有趣结合，允许玩家体验独特的太空世界，并创造自己的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166890/extras/ec734d5443e27f976673490c8832c1ea.webp?t=1763028353\" width=605 height=60 /></span></p>",
